@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-fabrication#> .
@prefix bs: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-fabrication>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:imports <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core> ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar Fabrication Model" ;
  rdfs:comment "AOT compilation of (O,Σ,P) → (G,K,E); CPU default, GPU optional, deterministic builds." .

### Fabrication backends
:Fabricator a owl:Class .
:CPUBackend a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :Fabricator .
:GPUBackend a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :Fabricator .
:HybridBackend a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :Fabricator .

### Fabrication modes  
:FabricationMode a owl:Class .
:mode a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range :FabricationMode .
:cpuMode a :FabricationMode .
:gpuMode a :FabricationMode .
:hybridMode a :FabricationMode .

### Input packs
:OntologyPack a owl:Class .
:ShapePack a owl:Class .
:PatternPack a owl:Class .
:consumes a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range [
  a owl:Class ; owl:unionOf ( :OntologyPack :ShapePack :PatternPack ) ] .

### Output artifacts (G,K,E)
:FabricationArtifact a owl:Class .
:producesGraph a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range bs:ExecutionGraph .
:producesKernel a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range bs:Kernel .
:producesEnvelope a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range bs:Envelope .
:produces a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range :FabricationArtifact .

### Determinism guarantees
:deterministicBuild a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:varianceNs a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range xsd:decimal .
:byteIdentical a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :FabricationArtifact ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### Compilation metadata
:compilationDigest a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :FabricationArtifact ; rdfs:range xsd:hexBinary .
:toolchainVersion a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range xsd:string .
:reproducibleBuild a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Fabricator ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .